parameters: Clea: It's quite creepy here, isn't it?

Thief Nora: It has a nasty smell that's different from
animals... Ugh, are we really going inside...?

Mage Relm: It's absolutely impossible for that warrior of
Valt to avoid a place and also prohibit combat!

Thief Perno: ...What we need to deliver to the deepest
part is the orc's treasure, an axe.

Thief Perno: With my current abilities, I can't use magic
to completely erase everyone's presence and reach the
deepest part.
Mage Relm: T-Then, what should we do!?

Thief Perno: But if it's just you, who can manage somehow,
I think we can reach the deepest part together.

Thief Nora: A-Are you talking about me!? That's impossible,
you know? I've always been called a hopeless thief.

Thief Perno: That's just the usual way for ordinary
thieves, so you have your own way.

Thief Perno: With my excellent sense of smell and hearing,
I can vouch for Thief Perno... You can have confidence in
me.

Thief Nora: A-Although I'm scared, really scared, I'll do
my best.
Clea: Are you really okay, Nora-san?

Thief Nora: I'm so happy to be acknowledged, so I want to
live up to expectations... Is that not possible?
Clea: I understand, Nora-san should be able to do it.

Thief Perno: Hehe, it's settled then. When you're ready,
please let me know.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Phoni the Phantom Thief: Are you ready to make the return?

Phantom Thief Perno: It's natural to feel nervous. Let me
know when you're ready.

Phantom Thief Perno: I'm going to use magic now to make it
harder for the orcs to notice us...

Phantom Thief Perno: I'll entrust the axe to you for now. I
can't move while carrying luggage...
Thief Nora: Yes, I've been entrusted with it!

Phantom Thief Perno: Be careful, it was written in the
diary that the orcs have some level of intelligence.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Thief Nora: I'm back~ It was scary, you know!
Thief Nora: Perno-san, are you okay!?

Thief Perno: Haa haa... I-I'm fine... Just feeling a bit
heavy.

Thief Nora: The monsters have become even more noisy than
before!
Thief Perno: I'm sorry... My magic has run out...

Clea: I judge that this place has become dangerous. Shall
we return to the campus? Is that alright?

Thief Perno: I'm sorry, but I won't be able to properly
thank you in my current state...
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Clea (Let's not go in now, as we can hear the voices of
monsters.)
